  * test/gemutilities.rb: Added missing require for gem uninstall

2010-09-12  raggi <jftucker@gmail.com>

  * lib/rubygems.rb, test/test_gem.rb: Fix Gem.bin_path to support and
  correctly error when binfiles are not present in newer gems. Fixes #28411.
  Also fixup a number of bin_path tests and cleanup exceptions raised for
  certain cases.

2010-07-21  John Barnette <jbarnette@gmail.com>

  * lib/rubygems/requirement.rb, test/test_gem_requirement.rb: Teach ~> to
  respect lower-bound prerelease versions.

2010-07-10  Luis Lavena <luislavena@gmail.com>

  * ChangeLog, test/test_gem.rb: Expand Windows home candidates. RF #28371

2010-07-09  Aaron Patterson <aaron.patterson@gmail.com>

  * lib/rubygems/specification.rb, test/test_gem_specification.rb: removing the
  unused "current_version" variable

2010-06-09  Eric Lindvall <eric@5stops.com>

  * lib/rubygems/commands/install_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/install_update_options.rb, test/gemutilities.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_install_command.rb: Add --conservative option.  "Don't
  attempt to upgrade gems already meeting version requirement"

2010-06-30  raggi <jftucker@gmail.com>

  * lib/rubygems/version.rb: Speed up Gem::Version#<=> by 2-3x in common cases.
  Good for bundler etc. Additional credit to Aman Gupta (tmm1) for providing
  some of the included optimisations and benchmark cases:
  http://gist.github.com/458185

2011-05-14  Loren Segal <lsegal@soen.ca>

  * lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Add calling of Gem.post_build_hooks and allow
  pre_install_hooks/post_build_hooks to cancel gem install if they return false

  * .gitignore: Ignore doc files

  * README.md: Move notes about fork to bottom of readme

  * .yardopts, README.md: Forgot to add README/.yardopts

  * .document, History.txt, README, cruise_config.rb, slimgems.gemspec: Add
  .yardopts, make it README.md

  * GPL.txt, History.txt, LICENSE.txt, README, RUBYGEMS.rdoc,
  lib/rubygems/command_manager.rb, lib/rubygems/commands/setup_command.rb,
  slimgems.gemspec: Update README, history, etc.

2011-05-13  Loren Segal <lsegal@soen.ca>

  * lib/rubygems.rb, slimgems.gemspec: Update method for getting SlimGems
  version in gemspec

