2009-06-15  Chad Woolley <thewoolleyman@gmail.com>

  * lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: bump version to be greater than released
  version.  See
  http://rubyforge.org/pipermail/rubygems-developers/2009-June/004719.html 

  * Manifest.txt, lib/rubygems.rb, lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: move
  RubyGems version declaration back into lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb, so
  third-party tools which run tests against trunk of RubyGems can load it
  explicitly before system rubygems version is loaded. 

  * Manifest.txt: add install_build_dependencies.rb to manifest 

  * ChangeLog, cruise_config.rb, install_build_dependencies.rb: Add
  install_build_dependencies.rb, update cruise_config.rb to call it before
  running build. 

