2009-06-10  Phil Hagelberg <phil@hagelb.org>

  * lib/rubygems/install_update_options.rb, lib/rubygems/installer.rb,
  test/test_gem_installer.rb: Remove auto-fallback of installation to ~/.gem
  when Gem.home isn't writable.  This behaviour was too easy to trigger
  accidentally. Use the --user-install flag if you want things put in your home
  directory. 

  * test/test_gem_indexer.rb: Fixed RSS test. Maybe it could be made less
  brittle? 

  * test/test_gem_commands_dependency_command.rb: Fix dependency command test. 

  * test/test_gem_commands_uninstall_command.rb: Fix uninstall command test. 

  * lib/rubygems/indexer.rb, lib/rubygems/source_index.rb,
  test/test_gem_indexer.rb, test/test_gem_source_index.rb: Fixed indexer to use
  released_gems instead of all gems when building indices. 

  * lib/rubygems/spec_fetcher.rb, test/test_gem_spec_fetcher.rb: Make
  SpecFetcher's "all" methods return released versions only. 

  * lib/rubygems/source_index.rb: Merge @gems and @prerelease_gems in
  SourceIndex. Search methods should make distinction.  Still need to fix test
  cases. 

  * test/test_gem_commands_uninstall_command.rb: Added failing test case for
  bug #26069. 

