  util_setup_fake_fetcher. 

  * lib/rubygems/indexer.rb, test/test_gem_indexer.rb: Fixed Indexer's update
  to handle prereleases correctly. 

  * lib/rubygems/indexer.rb, test/test_gem_indexer.rb: Update Indexer to handle
  prerelease gems correctly.  Still needs a few more tests. 

  * lib/rubygems/source_index.rb, lib/rubygems/spec_fetcher.rb,
  test/gemutilities.rb, test/test_gem_dependency_installer.rb,
  test/test_gem_source_index.rb, test/test_gem_spec_fetcher.rb: Fixed
  SpecFetcher to handle prerelease gems and update a number of tests. 

