  prerelease-index tests. 

  * lib/rubygems/dependency_installer.rb, lib/rubygems/spec_fetcher.rb,
  test/test_gem_dependency_installer.rb: Propagate prerelease flag all the way
  up to SpecFetcher#list method. 

  * lib/rubygems/indexer.rb, lib/rubygems/source_index.rb,
  test/test_gem_indexer.rb, test/test_gem_source_index.rb: Keep a third index
  for prerelease gems only.  The SourceIndex keeps prerelease gems in a
  separate list. The Indexer uses that separate list to build a
  prerelease_specs_index. 

  * lib/rubygems/source_index.rb, test/test_gem_source_index.rb,
  test/test_gem_specification.rb: SourceIndex keeps prerelease gems in separate
  list internally. 

  * lib/rubygems/specification.rb: Prerelease gems should require rubygems >=
  1.4.0, not > 1.3.1. 

