  download method, and made file URI handling actually work 

2009-01-21  Daniel Berger <djberg96@gmail.com>

  * lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb: Removed the file_uri? method - just use
  URI#scheme == 'file' 

2009-01-19  Daniel Berger <djberg96@gmail.com>

  * ChangeLog: Added changes for uri scheme validation in the remote_fetcher.rb
  file and corresponding changes to the test_gem_remote_fetcher.rb file 

  * lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb: Added uri scheme validation back into the
  open_uri_or_path method, though now it accepts https and file, and has a
  slightly different error message 

  * test/test_gem_remote_fetcher.rb: Updated the expected error message in the
  test_fetch_size_bad_uri test 

2009-01-18  Daniel Berger <djberg96@gmail.com>

  * lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb: Updated the open_uri_or_path method to
  return data, instead of the path, for file uri's 

2009-01-17  Daniel Berger <djberg96@gmail.com>

  * lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb: Update file uri handling in the
  open_uri_or_path method 

  * lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb: Made second '/' character optional in the
  regex in file_uri?, since it won't be present if no hostname is provided 

  * lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb: Removed a type check in the
  open_uri_or_path since that already happens up front in the option parser 

  * ChangeLog: Added file URL handling changes in remote_fetcher.rb and
  local_remote_options.rb 

  * lib/rubygems/local_remote_options.rb: Allow file urls 

  * lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb: Removed the get_file_uri_path method - the
  URI#path method does this already Changed the file_uri? method to call .to_s
  on its argument first in case it's a URI object and not a String 

2009-01-15  Daniel Berger <djberg96@gmail.com>

  * ChangeLog: Added note regarding test skippage for test_gem_installer.rb and
  test_gem_install_update_options.rb 

  * test/test_gem_installer.rb: The test_generate_bin_script_no_perms and
  test_generate_bin_symlink_no_perms tests are now skipped on MS Windows 

  * test/test_gem_install_update_options.rb: The
  test_user_install_disabled_read_only test is now skipped on MS Windows 

  * ChangeLog: Added note regarding test skippage for
  test/test_gem_doc_manager.rb on MS Windows 

  * test/test_gem_doc_manager.rb: The test_uninstall_doc_unwritable test is now
  skipped on MS Windows 

  * ChangeLog: Added comment regarding typo fix in the
  generate_index_command.rb file 

  * lib/rubygems/commands/generate_index_command.rb: Fixed a typo in the
  description 

  * ChangeLog: Added changes related to the addition of the license
  specification attribute - partial implementation of RF #11041 

  * lib/rubygems/specification.rb: Added validation for license information -
  licenses must be 64 characters or less 

  * lib/rubygems/commands/query_command.rb: Added license information to
  detailed output 

  * test/test_gem_specification.rb: Added tests for the license and licenses
  attribute, and updated a couple of other tests to accomodate the change 

  * lib/rubygems/specification.rb: Added the license(s) attribute, based on
  feature request RF #11041 

