2009-01-02  Daniel Berger <djberg96@gmail.com>

  * ChangeLog: Added note regarding RF bug #22598 - ensure
  specification_version is a Fixnum 

  * test/test_gem_specification.rb: Added tests that ensure that the
  specification_version must be a Fixnum - RF bug #22598 

  * lib/rubygems/specification.rb: Added validation to ensure
  specification_version is a Fixnum - fixes RF bug #22598 

  * ChangeLog: Added comment regarding RF bug #22151 - automatically normalize
  URI for HTTP_PROXY 

  * test/test_gem_remote_fetcher.rb: Added a test that validates the
  get_proxy_from_env automatically normalizes the uri - RF bug #22151 

  * lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb: The get_proxy_from_env method now
  normalizes the uri before parsing - RF bug #22151 

  * ChangeLog: Added fix for RF bug #22277 - duplicate sources should be
  ignored 

  * test/test_gem_local_remote_options.rb: Modified test to check for duplicate
  sources - RF bug #22277 

  * lib/rubygems/local_remote_options.rb: The add_source_option now ignores
  duplicates - RF bug #22277 

  * ChangeLog: Clarification - #23003 was a patch, not a bug 

  * ChangeLog: Added change regarding RF bug #23003 - Quote destination path if
  it contains spaces 

  * lib/rubygems/ext/rake_builder.rb: The destination path is now quoted if it
  contains spaces - RF bug #23003 

  * ChangeLog: Added note regarding RF bug #22313 - require 'etc' explicitly 

  * lib/rubygems.rb: Added an explicit require 'etc' at the top 

  * README: Added Daniel Berger as a contributor 

  * test/test_gem_platform.rb: Added some basic tests for the empty? method 

  * ChangeLog: Added comment regarding RF bug #22603 - Undefined empty? method
  for Gem::Platform 

  * lib/rubygems/platform.rb: Added an empty? method to deal with gems created
  prior to 0.9.5, which are not plain strings 

