2008-12-31  Daniel Berger <djberg96@gmail.com>

  * ChangeLog: Added fix for RF patch #22532 - target dir not honored 

  * lib/rubygems/commands/unpack_command.rb: Applied RF patch #22532 - target
  dir not honored 

