  scheme 

  * lib/rubygems/local_remote_options.rb: Allow https as a valid scheme 

  * ChangeLog: Added change regarding bug #22764 - Etc.getpwuid might return
  nil on certain platforms 

  * lib/rubygems.rb: Modified the set_paths method to check for the possibility
  of Etc.getpwuid returning nil on certain platforms 

