  Gem.user_home does not exist 

  * lib/rubygems/defaults.rb: The default path now falls back to only the
  default_dir if Gem.user_home does not exist 

  * ChangeLog: Added change regarding RF bug #19136 - don't allow a .gem file
  to be added onto itself 

  * lib/rubygems/builder.rb: No longer allows .gem file to be added to itself 

