  test/test_gem_commands_install_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_query_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_sources_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_specification_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_update_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_dependency_installer.rb, test/test_gem_gem_path_searcher.rb,
  test/test_gem_outdated_command.rb, test/test_gem_source_index.rb,
  test/test_gem_source_info_cache.rb, test/test_gem_spec_fetcher.rb: Switch
  Gem::SpecFetcher#fetch to be compatible with
  Gem::SourceInfoCache#search_with_source.  Update Gem::DependencyInstaller,
  Gem::SourceIndex, dep, outdated, query, sources and update commands to use
  SpecFetcher.  

