2007-11-23  Richard Kilmer <rich@infoether.com>

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems.rb, lib/rubygems/installer.rb,
  lib/rubygems/platform.rb, lib/rubygems/require_paths_builder.rb,
  test/gemutilities.rb, test/test_gem_installer.rb, util/gem_prelude.rb: made
  changes to support rubygems fast loading on ruby 1.9.  created
  util/gem_prelude.rb which adds all highest level gems require_paths onto the
  load path and then faults in the full rubygems library if any Gem constant or
  method is called.  centralized all Config::CONFIG options into
  Gem::ConfigMap. 

