  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/commands/fetch_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/install_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/outdated_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/dependency_installer.rb, lib/rubygems/platform.rb,
  lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb, lib/rubygems/source_index.rb,
  lib/rubygems/source_info_cache.rb, lib/rubygems/specification.rb,
  lib/rubygems/version_option.rb, test/test_gem_platform.rb,
  test/test_gem_remote_fetcher.rb, test/test_gem_source_index.rb,
  test/test_gem_specification.rb, test/test_gem_version_option.rb: When
  --platform is given, always include Gem::Platforms::RUBY platform, and allow
  RUBY platform as an option.  Gems with non-RUBY platforms sort last (first in
  preference for installation).  Allow Gem::Platforms::match to match legacy
  platforms.  Add only_platform option to Gem::SourceIndex#search.  

