2007-08-18  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/commands/install_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/dependency_list.rb, lib/rubygems/source_index.rb,
  lib/rubygems/version.rb, test/test_gem_commands_build_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_dependency.rb, test/test_gem_dependency_list.rb,
  test/test_gem_requirement.rb, test/test_gem_source_info_cache.rb,
  test/test_gem_specification.rb, test/test_gem_version.rb: Search
  Gem::SourceIndex and Gem::SourceInfoCache by Gem::Dependenency.  Gem::Version
  can be created via String or Integer.  Gem::Requirement::default is now >= 0.
   Gem::Requirement can be built from a Gem::Dependency.  Gem::DependencyList
  uses TSort now.  Add Gem::DependencyList#fill_dependencies.  

  * lib/rubygems/dependency_list.rb, test/test_gem_dependency_list.rb: Fix bug
  where dependency_order had no entries due to no dependencies in list. 

  * lib/rubygems/commands/install_command.rb, test/gemutilities.rb,
  test/test_gem_command_manager.rb, test/test_gem_commands_install_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_installer.rb: Some tests for Gem::Commands::InstallCommand 

2007-08-17  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/dependency_list.rb,
  test/test_gem_dependency_list.rb: For diamond dependencies with different
  versions on the bottom of the diamond, trim all but the latest dependency. 
  This will prevent gems like hoe from being installed multiple times.  

  * lib/rubygems/dependency_list.rb, test/test_gem_dependency_list.rb: Clean up
  tests a bit 

  * lib/rubygems/dependency_list.rb, test/test_gem_dependency_list.rb: Heckle
  and sort. 

