2007-08-11  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * lib/rubygems/doc_manager.rb: Moved DocumentError to Gem::DocumentError like
  it used to be. 

  * doc/signing_gems.txt, lib/rubygems/exceptions.rb,
  lib/rubygems/gem_openssl.rb, lib/rubygems/security.rb: Move
  doc/signing_gems.txt into lib/rubygems/security.rb for great RDoc! 
  rubygems/security.rb now only holds Gem::Security and friends.  

  * lib/rubygems/commands/install_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/update_command.rb, lib/rubygems/gem_runner.rb,
  lib/rubygems/install_update_options.rb: Fix arguments as string in ~/.gemrc 

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/commands/sources_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/config_file.rb, test/test_gem_config_file.rb: Command-line args
  configuration args now override ~/.gemrc now. Gem.sources is pulled from
  ~/.gemrc now. Gem::ConfigFile can write itself out now.  `gem sources` now
  writes out Gem.configuration on changes. `gem sources --list` no longer
  checks source cache.   

  * lib/rubygems/config_file.rb, test/test_configfile.rb,
  test/test_gem_config_file.rb: Clean up tests for Gem::ConfigFile 

