  multiple times. 

2007-08-09  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems.rb, lib/rubygems/commands/query_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/config_file.rb, lib/rubygems/local_remote_options.rb,
  lib/rubygems/source_info_cache.rb, test/gemutilities.rb, test/test_gem.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_environment_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_query_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_local_remote_options.rb, test/test_gem_source_info_cache.rb,
  test/test_source_index.rb, test/test_user_interaction.rb: Make
  Gem::SourceInfoCache#search only search gems in Gem.sources. Make
  Gem::configuration a real Gem::ConfigFile object. Fix `gem query --details`.
  Add `gem query --no-versions`. Make `gem mumble --source URL` only use that
  source. Fix Gem::ConfigFile#[]= to match Gem::ConfigFile#[].  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems.rb, lib/rubygems/commands/environment_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/source_info_cache.rb, pkgs/sources/lib/sources.rb,
  pkgs/sources/sources.gemspec, post-install.rb, test/functional.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_environment_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_source_info_cache.rb: Death of the 'sources' gem.  RubyGems now
  attempts to load the sources gem and falls back to calling
  Gem::default_sources.  

  * lib/rubygems/source_index.rb, test/functional.rb, test/gemenvironment.rb,
  test/gemutilities.rb, test/test_builder.rb, test/test_check_command.rb,
