  test/test_file_list.rb, test/test_format.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_build_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_cert_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_contents_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_dependency_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_commands_specification_command.rb,
  test/test_gem_outdated_command.rb, test/test_gem_source_info_cache.rb,
  test/test_gem_source_info_cache_entry.rb, test/test_gemloadpaths.rb,
  test/test_installer.rb, test/test_package.rb, test/test_parse_commands.rb,
  test/test_process_commands.rb, test/test_remote_fetcher.rb,
  test/test_source_index.rb, test/test_specification.rb,
  test/test_validator.rb, test/test_version_comparison.rb: Pushed dependencies
  down as far as they could reasonably go.  Removed Gem::manage_gems.  Fixed
  functional tests.  Added tests for `gem cert`, `gem build`.  Added
  rubygems/extensions.rb, common place for all extensions.  

2007-07-30  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Add note about why we add the additional .cmd
  bin scripts on windows. 

2007-07-26  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/commands/sources_command.rb: Fix spelling error. 
  Fixes Bug #11064 by Chris Eskow.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/version.rb, test/test_gem_version.rb: Disallow
  newlines in version string.  Strip spaces from version string.  Fixes Bug
  #9499 by Bryce Kerley.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb, test/test_remote_fetcher.rb: An
  empty HTTP_PROXY means no proxy.  Fixes Bug #9042 by Michael Brodhead.  

  * ChangeLog, post-install.rb: Make sure we use the latest-and-greatest
  RubyGems when running post-install.rb. Fixes Bug #8411 by Duy Nguyen.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/config_file.rb: Add ConfigFile#[]=, so --proxy
  command-line option works.  Fixes #8152 by Justin Sabelkko.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/commands/pristine_command.rb: Compare
  fully-qualified paths.  Fixes bug #7976 by Lyle Johnson.  

  * ChangeLog, test/test_gem_ext_configure_builder.rb: Linux has different
  behavior for `sh ./configure` when configure is missing. Fix adpated from
  Patch #10019 by Donavan Pantke.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/commands/install_command.rb: Don't raise an error
  when a gem has no tests.  Patch #11824 by Katsuyuki MIYAMUKO.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb: Support HTTP Basic
  authentication.  Patch #8121 by Max Dunn.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/custom_require.rb: Only rescue a LoadError that
  matches the file we are requiring.  Patch #10723 by Tyler Rick.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/commands/install_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/validator.rb: Output test failures when using install -t.  Patch
  #10659 by Paul Brannan.  Fix bug in `gem install` when passing passing
  options to uninstaller on failed test run.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/user_interaction.rb, test/test_configfile.rb,
  test/test_user_interaction.rb: If stdin is not a tty, it is unlikely that gem
  is going to get a response when asking a question.  Patch #10660 by Paul
  Brannan.  Hack around test that breaks if you turn on backtrace in ~/.gemrc  

  * ChangeLog: Forgot to submit ChangeLog :/ 

  * lib/rubygems/commands/generate_index_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/abstract_index_builder.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/compressor.rb, lib/rubygems/indexer/indexer.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/master_index_builder.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/quick_index_builder.rb: Create the index in /tmp, then
  move it into place when we're done.  This will prevent spurious bulk index
  updates from occurring during index.  Remove the option to not build the
  quick index.  Everybody loves the quick index.  Fix name of class for yaml
  index.  Gem::Cache is long gone.  Compress files before writing.  

2007-07-24  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * lib/rubygems/commands/mirror_command.rb, lib/rubygems/config_file.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/indexer.rb, lib/rubygems/source_index.rb: Print out
  extra crap when in really_verbose mode to know what updating does. Finish
  progress correctly. 

  * lib/rubygems/version.rb: Fix Gem::Version RDoc. Make sure
  Gem::Version::Requirement doesn't show up in RDoc. 

  * lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb, lib/rubygems/source_index.rb,
  lib/rubygems/specification.rb, lib/rubygems/version.rb: Switch
  Gem::Version::Requirment to the replacement Gem::Requirement 

  * test/test_builder.rb, test/test_installer.rb: Don't litter the trunk with
  test files.  

  * lib/rubygems/commands/dependency_command.rb: Correctly report gems not
  found.  Work with really old/broken gem dependencies.  Fix remote/local
  default.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/command.rb, test/test_command.rb: Don't worry about
  duplicated commmand-line options, OptionParser takes care of it for us.  

