   Patch by Jeremy Burks.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/user_interaction.rb, test/test_user_interaction.rb:
  Check for EOF on Gem::UserInteraction#choose_from_list.  Fixes bug #8018.
  Patch by Jos Backus.  

