  test/test_gem_commands_contents_command.rb, test/test_source_index.rb,
  test/test_specification.rb: Add --lib-only option and remove useless --list
  option in `gem contents`.  Restrict Gem::Specification#lib_files to files in
  #require_paths.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/outdated_command.rb,
