  test/io_capture.rb, test/test_file_list.rb, test/test_installer.rb: Use
  UserInteraction for output instead of puts.  Pull backtrace, benchmark from
  config file.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/commands/generate_index_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer.rb, lib/rubygems/indexer/abstract_index_builder.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/announcer.rb, lib/rubygems/indexer/indexer.rb: Remove
  Gem::Indexer::Announcer in favor of Gem::UserInteraction.  Use progress_meter
  while indexing gems.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/environment_command.rb, lib/rubygems/config_file.rb:
  Allow configuration settings to be examined in `gem env` Allow "really
  verbose" mode to be entered, so the verbose progress meter works. Allow
  verbose to be set from ~/.gemrc  

  * : update_rubygems is executable 

  * ChangeLog, bin/gemri: Everybody should have ri integration now. 

  * ChangeLog, bin/index_gem_repository.rb, lib/rubygems/command_manager.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/generate_index_command.rb, lib/rubygems/indexer.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/abstract_index_builder.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/announcer.rb, lib/rubygems/indexer/compressor.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/indexer.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/master_index_builder.rb,
  lib/rubygems/indexer/quick_index_builder.rb: Move `index_gem_repository.rb`
  into `gem generate_index`.  Extracted index_gem_repository.rb's Indexer into
  Gem::Indexer::*.  Backtrace is now printed with --debug.  Gem::Command no
  longer infinitely loops if a command can't be loaded. (Developer-visible
  only.)  

  * lib/rubygems/commands/lock_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/mirror_command.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/which_command.rb,
  test/test_documentation_generation.rb: Commit forgotten test fix.  Capitalize
  command summaries.  Require open-uri on execute for mirror command.  (This
  may still be wrong.)  

  * ChangeLog, bin/gem_server, lib/rubygems/command_manager.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/server_command.rb, lib/rubygems/doc_manager.rb,
  lib/rubygems/server.rb: Move `gem_server` under `gem`.  Only raise
  Gem::FilePermissionError when attempting to work with the documentation
  directory.  Remove option processing from Gem::Server, now in
  Gem::Commands::ServerCommand.   

  * lib/rubygems/commands/lock_command.rb: Don't need to pass options around
  anymore 

  * ChangeLog, bin/gemlock, lib/rubygems/command_manager.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/lock_command.rb: Move `gemlock` under `gem`.  

  * ChangeLog, bin/gem_mirror, lib/rubygems/command_manager.rb,
  lib/rubygems/commands/mirror_command.rb: Move `gem_mirror` under `gem`. Fetch
  yaml.Z index instead of yaml index to be nice to mirrors. Be friendlier to
  windows users by using File.join.  

