  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: Bumped version to 0.9.0.9.   

  * ChangeLog, Rakefile, lib/rubygems/specification.rb, test/gemenvironment.rb,
  test/test_specification.rb: Enhanced the files and default_executable methods
  on specification to be a bit more resistant to pathologically bad input data
  (in response to input from the JRuby community). Also some small Rakefile
  cleanups.   

