2006-11-30  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/installer.rb, lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb,
  test/gemutilities.rb, test/test_remote_installer.rb,
  test/test_source_index.rb: Ensure gems with similar names cannot be matched
  for install.  This was broken when searching was removed from
  RemoteInstaller. Return extension-building results in Exception on build
  failure.  

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/installer.rb, lib/rubygems/remote_fetcher.rb,
  lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb, lib/rubygems/specification.rb,
  lib/rubygems/validator.rb, lib/rubygems/version.rb, post-install.rb:
  post-install.rb requires rbconfig. Fix several ivar warnings caused by YAML
  loaded specs. Ensure that the current directory is returned to. Raise
  more-helpful and less-deadly errors from RemoteFetcher, RemoteInstaller.
  Don't double-require open-uri. Create version requirement correctly in
  RemoteInstaller. Allow RemoteInstaller to work with SilentUI.  

