2006-08-22  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * ChangeLog, lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: Changed proxy arg to
  fetcher_class.new to use the @options[:http_proxy] rather than the @proxy_uri
  attribute.  The @proxy_uri value was never set.  Tried the proxy option using
  --http-proxy, the ENV var http_proxy and with no proxy.  

