  datadir methods  

2006-04-07  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: bumped to 0.8.11.15  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: Prettied up some code.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/doc_manager.rb: Backtrace stackdump now written to
  standard error.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: Added --ri/--no-ri option to install
  command. Refactored the rdoc generation to remove a bit of duplication. Added
  RI doc geneation to the rdoc command.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/doc_manager.rb: Moved note about RI/RDOC order to
  method level comments.  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: Updated changelog.  

2006-04-06  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/source_index.rb: added arg to from_installed_gems for
  backwards compatibility  

2006-04-05  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb,
  rubygems/test/test_parse_commands.rb: unit tests now assert install dir
  should be absolute  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: Dropped ancient TODO. Generate all
  RI docs before any RDoc docs.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/doc_manager.rb: Support generating all RI docs first.
   

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: Updated change log.  

  * rubygems/bin/gemlock, rubygems/lib/rubygems.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb, rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: Gemlock now generates gem commands
  instead of require_gem.  

  * rubygems/bin/gem_server: Removed ## style comments.  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: Updated change log.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: bumped version to 0.8.11.11  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Fixed typo in
  ExtExtConfBuilder  

2006-04-04  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/lib/rubygems/incremental_fetcher.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: defaults to bulk update for over
  50 gems  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/specification.rb, rubygems/test/bogussources.rb,
  rubygems/test/functional.rb, rubygems/test/test_specification.rb: fixed bug
  in 183 yaml support.  cleaned up specification.rb comments a bit.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: bumped to version 0.8.11.9  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/lib/rubygems/specification.rb: added code to
  make 1.8.3 generated gems digestible on a 1.8.4 system.  

