2006-03-29  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/specification.rb: removed unneeded require "date"
  from specification.rb.  We now use Time instead of Date.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: bumped version to 0.8.11.7  

  * rubygems/test/functional.rb: added warning to functional test of openssl
  not available  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb,
  rubygems/test/test_remote_fetcher.rb: Switch to using http_proxy in tests due
  to warning from open-uri  

