  extensions  

2006-03-18  Ryan Davis <ryand-ruby@zenspider.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/source_index.rb: Little hyper-annoying bugs squashed  

2006-02-26  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb, rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/open-uri.rb, rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb,
  rubygems/test/gemutilities.rb, rubygems/test/test_gempaths.rb,
  rubygems/test/test_installer.rb, rubygems/test/test_remote_fetcher.rb: Add
  support for proxy with authorization.  Changes: - Import open-uri from Ruby's
  CVS HEAD - Added proxy authorization discovery from proxy URL or from
  HTTP_PROXY_USER and HTTP_PROXY_PATH environment variables.  Includes tests. -
  Fix Rubygems tests on Windows.  

2006-02-24  Eric Hodel <drbrain@segment7.net>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/doc_manager.rb: Add ri data generation ability to the
  doc manager.  This needs a patch to ri for ri to pick it up, but ri data will
  be easily installable and uninstallable along with the rest of the package. 
  Remove methods that are no longer referenced by the rest of Rubygems.  

