2005-12-03  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: Bumped version.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: Removed incidental debug file
  generation.  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: Updated change log.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/config_file.rb: Added verbose option to ConfigFile.
  Not sure I like it. Reformatted comments a bit. Make --traceback an alias for
  --backtrace ... I can never remember which it is.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/user_interaction.rb: Added variations on the progress
  reporter: Silent, Simple and Verbose.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: Refactored spec conversion a
  bit.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/incremental_fetcher.rb: Improved error message when
  source cache info entry is bad.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_runner.rb: Made the GemRunner accept some DI like
  options.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: Added comments to some of the mixin
  modules for commands. Removed attempting messages.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/command.rb: Added abstract execute method. Added
  comments to methods. Refactored the specific_extra_args a bit. Reformatted
  some code.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/cmd_manager.rb: Added comments to Exceptions.
  Commented some methods. Allow multiple spaces between arguments. Removed
  obsolete load_config_file_options method.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems.rb: Added access to the standard configuration in the
  Gem module. (e.g. Gem.configuration)  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: Added abbreviation "rf" for "rubyfiles" in Rakefile.  

