2005-11-21  Chad Fowler <chad@chadfowler.com>

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/lib/rubygems.rb: Allow 0.0.0 to be a valid gem
  version (Ara Howard)  

2005-11-19  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/source_index.rb: Fixed comments.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: fixed comments.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: Added some comments.  

  * rubygems/test/test_incremental_fetcher.rb: Made the UI silent during
  testing. Added test for failures during incremental download.a  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/user_interaction.rb: Added a progress report to the
  UI. Added SilentUI (mainly for testing).  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/incremental_fetcher.rb: Added progress reporting to
  the incremental fetcher. Refactored incremental fetcher to determine the
  complete list of missing gems first. Added code to handle missing gemspecs in
  incremental download.  

2005-11-18  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/test/test_incremental_fetcher.rb: Added test for basic fetching.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: Bumped version to 0.8.11.4  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/incremental_fetcher.rb: Added comments to the
  incremental fetcher. Added a fetch_path method. Added a get_entry to handle
  the conversion of old cache entries into modern SourceInfoCacheEntry
  versions. Removed fetch (since we needed fetch_path anyways).  

  * rubygems/bin/generate_yaml_index.rb: removed generate_yaml_index  

  * rubygems/bin/index_gem_repository.rb: added index_gem_repository  

  * rubygems/test/test_incremental_fetcher.rb: Rewrote the incremental fetcher
  tests to use the new FlexMock syntax. (and I really like the result).  

  * rubygems/test/gemutilities.rb: Make sure the RubyGemTestCase calls the
  super setup.  

  * rubygems/test/functional_generate_yaml_index.rb: generate_yaml_index is now
  called index_gem_repository. Non-zipped gemspecs are no longer provided in
  the quick index.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/source_index.rb: Updated return type comment on
  +installed_spec_directories+. Added add_spec and remove_spec to interface.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: SourceIndex now supports a
  replace_source_index command (used by the incremental fetcher). Added
  comments on cache data format. The cached fetcher now uses an incremental
  fetcher. Removed require_gem on sources, we now just require sources
  directly.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/incremental_fetcher.rb: Rewrote the incremental
  fetcher from scratch to conform to unit tests.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/cmd_manager.rb: Added catching of timeout errors to
  the gem command top level.  

