2005-07-09  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: Bumped version to 0.8.10.101.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/builder.rb: Make sure signing_key is defined in spec
  before using.  

  * rubygems/post-install.rb: Provided backup if Gem.ruby is not defined.  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: Added signing to rubygems-update gem (if CERT_DIR
  defined).  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_openssl.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: to beta version 0.8.10.100  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/package.rb: Added test for SSL availability.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/security.rb: Changed require of openssl to
  rubygems/gem_openssl. Added runtime checks for the availability of SSL. Fixed
  constant references in load time code to use our own constants.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/package.rb: *** empty log message ***  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/builder.rb: Changed require of openssl to
  rubygems/gem_openssl.  

  * rubygems/test/fake_certlib/openssl.rb: added fake cert library for testing
  w/o ssl  

  * rubygems/test/functional.rb: Changed all function tests (except those
  testing cert and signing) to run without ssl available.  

  * rubygems/doc/release_notes/rel_0_8_11.rdoc,
  rubygems/scripts/upload_gemdoc.rb: added script to upload the gemdoc hieraki
  data to the web page. Started 0.8.11 release notes.  

  * rubygems/scripts/gemdoc.data: Added cert information to the gemdoc.  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: Added logs directory to clobber list. Added task to
  upload the gemdoc hieraki documentation.  

  * rubygems/.cvsignore: Added some ignore files.  

