2005-05-30  Ryan Davis <ryand-ruby@zenspider.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/specification.rb,
  rubygems/test/test_specification.rb: RubyGems HackFest Story Card #10: NO
  MORE DATE! Use Time (truncated to midnight) instead of Date for the date
  attribute of a gemspec. Made comments fit on a screen of decent width. pair:
  Eric Hodel & Ryan Davis  

2005-05-29  Ryan Davis <ryand-ruby@zenspider.com>

  * rubygems/test/test_file_list.rb, rubygems/test/test_specific_extras.rb:
  Added.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Added a simple comment.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/cmd_manager.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: RubyGems HackFest Story Card #1, done
  by Doug, Aaron and Evan: Package List - provide a comprehensive full path
  list of files in a gem. Added inspect command to list files in gem.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/command.rb, rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_runner.rb:
  RubyGems HackFest Story Card #11, done by Aaron and Evan: Gem RC settings
  like .cvsrc Extend .gemrc to include options after the named commands, like
  .cvsrc.  

  * rubygems/test/gemutilities.rb: quick_gem only yields if a block is given.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb, rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb,
  rubygems/test/test_installer.rb, rubygems/test/test_parse_commands.rb:
  RubyGems HackFest Story Card #3: Binwrapper vs symlink w/ Windows support.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems.rb, rubygems/test/test_specification.rb: RubyGems
  HackFest Story Card #2: autorequire should be a list, not a string. Upcast
  spec.autorequire to an array and iterate over it requiring each. Added class
  TestSpecification with autorequire tests.  

  * rubygems/test/test_local_cache.rb: Moved TestLocalCache to RubyGemTestCase.
  Nuked all consts. Fixed all tests to no longer use test/temp. Rather
  extensive refactorings of duplicate code across all tests.  

  * rubygems/test/test_gempaths.rb: Moved TestGemPaths to RubyGemTestCase.
  Nuked all consts. Fixed all tests to no longer use test/temp.  

  * rubygems/test/test_cached_fetcher.rb: Moved TestCachedFetcher to
  RubyGemTestCase. Nuked all consts. Minor fixes.  

  * rubygems/test/gemutilities.rb: Added a new abstract TestCase class with
  temporary data setup and utilities. Pulled up a fair amount from
  TestLocalCache. Added utility methods to create gems on the fly.  

