2005-03-04  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: updated changelog  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Now passing option hash to installer
  object. Added checks for :all, :ignore and :executables options. Now removing
  executables /after/ the gem has been removed.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: Added --all, --ignore and
  --executables options to uninstall. Added cleanup command.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/cmd_manager.rb: Registered cleanup command.  

  * rubygems/bin/gemwhich: added gemwhich  

  * rubygems/test/test_remote_fetcher.rb: Moved sleep in test for
  remote_fetcher.  Sometimes fails on Jims laptop.  

  * rubygems/test/test_dependency_list.rb: Added DependencyList tests.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: Bumped intermediate version.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Cleanup up comments cosmetically.
  has_dependents? is now ok_to_remove?.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/dependency_list.rb: Added ability for a
  DependencyList to update from a SourceIndex. Added an ok_to_remove? method to
  assist when deleting gems. Beefed up the topological sort  algorithm.
  Top_level is gone, replaced by active_count. Added build_predecessors.  

