2004-12-29  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: ChangeLog updates  

  * rubygems/test/test_remote_installer.rb: Added a to-do note to a disabled
  test so that it is not forgotten.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: Changed the RemoteInstaller to
  take an options hash rather than individual options.  This will leave the
  interface more resilient to changes as more options are added (e.g.
  --install_dependencies).  

  * rubygems/test/test_specification.rb: Added test for array_attributes.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/specification.rb: Added array_attribute metacommand.
  Explicitly marked attributes that take arrays.  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: Updated comments.  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: updated
  changelog and modified version to a developement version.  

  * rubygems/test/test_gempaths.rb: Added tests to support the changes to
  ensure_gem_directories.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems.rb: Fixed the ensure_gem_subdirectories logic to
  write the directories when it can and to not complain when it can not.  

