2004-12-07  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/bin/gem_server, rubygems/lib/rubygems.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb, rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/validator.rb: Renamed Cache to SourceIndex  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/source_index.rb: Fixed bug in
  SourceIndex.from_installed_gems.  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: Added debug.log to clobber list.  

  * rubygems/.cvsignore: *** empty log message ***  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: fixed missing post_install.rb script  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: fixed tagging problem in release task  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: release task ready for trying (again)  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: release task ready for trying  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: working on release task  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: Updated changelog  

  * rubygems/test/test_specification.rb: Fixed test to avoid the __FILE__
  stuff.  Running tests from rakefile guarantees that the file paths start from
  the right location.  

  * rubygems/pkgs/sources/sources.gemspec: Made Gem.sources_spec idempotent.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/specification.rb: Added @@gather to
  Gem::Specification to facilitate proper loads. Added Specification.load.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/source_index.rb: Fixed comments "long name" => "full
  name".  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: Changed to use
  Gem.Specification.load.  

  * rubygems/post-install.rb: Using block version of chdir.  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: Removed building of sources.gem from Rakefile (it is
  done in the post install script (which I originally missed). Upgraded the DBG
  finder to include breakpoint.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/rubygems_version.rb: added external file for ruby
  version  

  * rubygems/test/test_local_cache.rb: Fixed default value of cache to be a
  hash.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: Minor change.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/package.rb: Added require stringio to package module.
   

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems.rb: Moved ruby version into a separate file to make
  updating easier.  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: Added rake task to create a new release (initial
  version). Changed PKG_FILES to include pkgs instead of packages (and exclude
  temp directories). Added task to generate sources.gem.  

