  * rubygems/test/test_cached_fetcher.rb: removed unneeded reference to
  flexmock  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb,
  rubygems/test/test_cached_fetcher.rb, rubygems/test/test_remote_fetcher.rb,
  rubygems/test/yaml_data.rb: baby steps toward user writable caches.  

2004-12-01  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: updated change log.  

  * rubygems/test/onegem.rb: added onegem for testing reuse.  

  * rubygems/test/test_remote_installer.rb: Fixed mock source_info/cache
  results. Added MockFetcher#fetch_path to support install testing, but did not
  complete. Fixed gem_hash references. Removed unneeded mock installer. Trying
  to move install into developement area (i.e. not production gem home).
  test_install disabled for the moment while we fix it.  

  * rubygems/test/functional.rb: Refacter one.gem into its own utility package
  for reuse in unit tests.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: Removed extraneous "then"s.  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: Added a few clobber targets that were missed.  

  * rubygems/.cvsignore, rubygems/test/test_remote_fetcher.rb: Added remoet
  testing unit test.  

  * rubygems/test/test_remote_installer.rb: MockFetcher now handles 2 args just
  like the real thing.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: RemoteSourceFetcher now fully
  supports HTTP proxy. The source YAML is reduced before parsing.  This might
  lessen the chance of running into the YAML bug on large sources.  

