2004-09-07  Chad Fowler <chad@chadfowler.com>

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/test/test_package.rb: Fixed unit tests  

2004-09-06  Richard Kilmer <rich@infoether.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: cleaned up the remote_installer
  some, and handle the case where you don't have sudo permission to write the
  source cache file out.  Output message when updating a source cache to let
  the use know what is going on.  

  * rubygems/test/test_remote_installer.rb: fixed change in api to remote
  installer (get_caches has a second argument)  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: search needed to be updated due
  to the new api  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: enabled
  caching of the source caches.  this dramatically increases the performance
  for remote installation  

2004-09-06  Chad Fowler <chad@chadfowler.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Changed windows batch file generation
  to include quotes in case there are spaces in the path to the ruby executable
  (rf bug #828  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Changed windows batch files per
  suggestion by Juha Pohjalainen  

