2004-07-15  Richard Kilmer <rich@infoether.com>

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/bin/gem: fixed the ARGV passing in bin/gem to
  ingore args past -- which are used for passing params to source gems
  (extconf.rb)  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/format.rb, rubygems/lib/rubygems/old_format.rb: added
  old_format.rb which is used in the (hack) in format.rb to detect the older
  version of a gem, and if present, switches to that class instead.  there is a
  commented out warning that can be commented in if folks want to warn if a gem
  of an old format is encountered.  

