  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/lib/rubygems.rb: * lib/rubygems.rb:
  (#require_gem) added the ability to do "require_gem 'rake/packagetask'", for
  instance, which is a shortcut for "require_gem 'rake'; require
  'rake/packagetask'".  

