  * rubygems/install.rb: do not install backup files  

2004-07-03  Jim Weirich <jim.weirich@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/scripts/specdoc.data: added category to specdoc.data  

  * rubygems/test/functional.rb: function tests use a missing config file by
  default  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: updated changelog  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: added some --no-xxxx version of the
  command to override the .gemrc file  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: updated changelog  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_runner.rb: Set the local rdoc options.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/doc_manager.rb: Removed old drive reference. Concat
  local rdoc options on the end. Added configured_args as a place to store
  local rdoc configuration.  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: handling extra args from config file  

  * rubygems/test/testgem.rc: Added some extra arguments.  

  * rubygems/test/test_command.rb: Added tests for command option recognition. 

  * rubygems/test/functional.rb: Added functional tests for extra args.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_runner.rb: Configuration handled in
  do_configuration now.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/command.rb: Added a handles? method to Command so
  that we can detect which extra arguments can be used with a command. New
  method (add_extra_args) to add the config files extra arguments to the front
  of the argument list. Added extra_args to Command class to hold the extra
  args discovered in the config file.  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: Added TEST=filename option to all the test targets.  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/lib/rubygems/config_file.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_runner.rb, rubygems/scripts/.cvsignore,
  rubygems/test/data/.cvsignore, rubygems/test/test_configfile.rb,
  rubygems/test/testgem.rc: added config_file and gem_runner  

  * rubygems/test/test_specification.rb: Added parens to get rid of warning.  

  * rubygems/test/functional.rb: added function test for gemrc.  

  * rubygems/scripts/gemdoc.data: Added an example to the specification
  command.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems.rb: Added runner and config file to manage_gems.
  use_paths now handles null parameters ok.  

  * rubygems/bin/gem: Top object is now the GemRunner rather than the command
  manager.  

  * rubygems/Rakefile: Added new temp test dir to clobber.  

