  * rubygems/Rakefile, rubygems/scripts/gemdoc.data: updated change log  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog: changelog updates  

  * rubygems/test/test_specification.rb: Tests beefed up to check for redundent
  files and rdoc files. Added test for validation of rubygem version.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/specification.rb: Removed concat in extra rdoc files
  setter. Added normalize to validate. Added normalize to handle normalization
  of file lists.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/gem_commands.rb: Fixed duplicate gem gem problem in
  several usage comments.  

