  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/builder.rb, rubygems/lib/rubygems/validator.rb:
  http:/
  5 File reads in binary mode for Windows.  

  * rubygems/test/functional.rb: Fixed functional test broken by Gavin's --help
  changes.  

