2004-05-01  Chad Fowler <chad@chadfowler.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/format.rb: Fixed bug due to changes in YAML error
  reporting.  Reported by Charles Comstock on ruby-talk.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Library stubs didn't work for
  autorequires that are under subdirectories.  Fixed.  Hard to test
  unfortunately.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: mkdir_p if File.dirname(target_file)
  for stub doesn't already exist.  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: *Actually* made installing of library
  stubs not the default this time.  

2004-04-30  Chad Fowler <chad@chadfowler.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Removed and unused variable pointed out
  by guillame dorchies at
  http://rubyforge.org/forum/forum.php?thread_id=710&forum_id=505  

  * rubygems/ChangeLog, rubygems/README, rubygems/Releases,
  rubygems/doc/DevDoc.html, rubygems/doc/GemSpecification.html,
  rubygems/doc/UserDoc.html: Removed local copies of documentation for now. 
  Will use the wiki until a non-alpha release.  Added ChangeLog and Releases
  file for distribution.  Modified README to reflect doc location changes and
  additional contributors.  

  * rubygems/bin/gem: --install-stub is no longer the default ;)  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Rich Kilmer (who kicks butt) figured
  out how to fix the library stub stuff.  

