  generator.  

2004-04-29  Gavin Sinclair <gsinclair@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Added skeleton code and comments to
  uninstall stub apps and libs  

  * rubygems/install.rb: Don't install library stub for 'sources'  

  * rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb: Improvements to library stub
  installation: * don't overwrite existing file (emit warning) * nice warning
  if there's a permission problem * observe --[no-]install-stub flag (rather,
  observe the argument to #install)  

  * rubygems/bin/gem: --install-stub is now the default  

