  test-breaking self. ;)  

2004-04-26  Gavin Sinclair <gsinclair@gmail.com>

  * rubygems/bin/gem, rubygems/lib/rubygems/installer.rb,
  rubygems/lib/rubygems/remote_installer.rb: Installing a gem now causes a
  library stub to be installed as well, allowing you to require 'package'
  without knowing it's a gem.  

